text:
Chicarron & Yuca Frita (4 stars);
Usually were good but the chicarron tasted different (in a bad way) the last time he had it, hopefully it's just a fluke. The yuca frita (fried yucca root) is the star though. 

Mixed grill (4 stars); 
Huge portion, need 3 persons to finish it. Taste good, especially the sausage. Looove the sausage.

Arepas - pork butt and garlic shrimp (5 stars);
You can have the garlic shrimp served cold or hot. I've tried both but personally like hot better. 

Place is clean, so is the restroom. Staff are always nice and polite.
